ZH: 他非常勤奋，每天早上都会起得很早。
EN: He is very diligent, he wakes up very early every morning.

ZH: 她勤奋地学习，成绩一直很好。
EN: She studies diligently and has always performed well academically.

ZH: 这个团队非常勤奋，每天都在努力工作。
EN: This team is very diligent and works hard every day.

ZH: 他勤奋地工作，总能在短时间内完成任务。
EN: He works diligently and always manages to complete tasks within a short period of time.

ZH: 她是一个勤奋的学生，从不浪费时间。
EN: She is a diligent student and never wastes time.

ZH: 这个公司的员工都非常勤奋，使公司迅速发展。
EN: The employees in this company are all very diligent and have contributed to its rapid growth.

