EN: He is very diligent and never procrastinates.

ZH: 她的勤奋使得她得到了晋升的机会。
EN: Her diligence has earned her the opportunity for a promotion.

ZH: 这位医生勤奋地工作，一个星期七天都不休息。
EN: This doctor works diligently and does not take a day off for seven days a week.

ZH: 她的勤奋使她在竞争激烈的行业中脱颖而出。
EN: Her diligence has allowed her to stand out in the highly competitive industry.

ZH: 这个学生勤奋地复习，考试取得了好成绩。
EN: This student revised diligently and achieved good results in the exam.

ZH: 他是一个勤奋的建筑师，每个项目都用心完成。
EN: He is a diligent architect who puts his heart into every project.

ZH: 她用勤奋和毅力克服了许多困难。
EN: She overcame many difficulties with diligence and perseverance.

