EN: This teacher is very diligent and always strives to help students grow.

ZH: 他的勤奋使得他赢得了尊重和信任。
EN: His diligence has earned him respect and trust.

ZH: 虽然他没有天赋，但他通过勤奋弥补了不足。
EN: Although he isn't talented, he compensates for it through diligence.

